  "texts": [
    "Using Masked Language Modeling (MLM), the model was trained using unstructured and semi-structured open-source Cyber Threat Intelligence (CTI) data.",
    "Its evaluation encompassed diverse downstream tasks with potential applications in Security Operations Centers (SOCs).",
    "They additionally offer real-world examples of how to apply CyBERT to cybersecurity problems.",
    "Several subsequent works have furthered the advancements of this research in terms of both training efficiency and accuracy such as SecureBERT [2], CySecBERT [6], and ClaimsBERT [4].",
    "In this regard, Bayer et al. [6] presented a word embedding model based on BERT and collected a dataset from multiple sources."
  ],
